, \"from\": 314, \"to\": 324}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I want to defend my title in 2028, and if I stay fit, I intend to participate in the 2032 Olympics as well,\\\" saidArshad Nadeem, highlighting his long-term goals after his historic achievement for Pakistan.\", \"from\": 326, \"to\": 531, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 522, \"end\": 530, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\", \"score\": 0.9996900697378169, \"rank\": 0.00029784964454692407, \"text\": \"Pakistan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my title\", \"from\": 343, \"to\": 351}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2032 Olympics\", \"from\": 407, \"to\": 424}, {\"ngram\": \"Nadeem\", \"from\": 446, \"to\": 452}, {\"ngram\": \"his long-term goals\", \"from\": 467, \"to\": 486}, {\"ngram\": \"his historic achievement\", \"from\": 493, \"to\": 517}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Arshad recounted the warm reception he received at Lahore Airport, where he was honoured by the Chief Minister, who visited his village, and the Prime Minister, who invited him to the PM House on Independence Day.\", \"from\": 533, \"to\": 746, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Arshad\", \"from\": 533, \"to\": 539}, {\"ngram\": \"the warm reception\", \"from\": 550, \"to\": 568}, {\"ngram\": \"Lahore Airport\", \"from\": 584, \"to\": 598}, {\"ngram\": \"the Chief Minister\", \"from\": 625, \"to\": 643}, {\"ngram\": \"his village\", \"from\": 657, \"to\": 668}, {\"ngram\": \"the Prime Minister\", \"from\": 674, \"to\": 692}, {\"ngram\": \"the PM House\", \"from\": 713, \"to\": 725}, {\"ngram\": \"Independence Day\", \"from\": 729, \"to\": 745}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He also thanked the Governor of Sindh, Kamran Tessori, for his respectful acknowledgement.\", \"from\": 747, \"to\": 837, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 779, \"end\": 784, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sindh\", \"score\": 0.9999935476822772, \"