\", \"from\": 1581, \"to\": 1598}, {\"ngram\": \"his medal-winning effort\", \"from\": 1625, \"to\": 1649}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have worked a lot on my run-up, and my physique gives me an advantage,\\\" he added, highlighting his focus on improving his technique.\", \"from\": 1652, \"to\": 1787, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my run-up\", \"from\": 1676, \"to\": 1685}, {\"ngram\": \"my physique\", \"from\": 1691, \"to\": 1702}, {\"ngram\": \"an advantage\", \"from\": 1712, \"to\": 1724}, {\"ngram\": \"his focus\", \"from\": 1750, \"to\": 1759}, {\"ngram\": \"his technique\", \"from\": 1773, \"to\": 1786}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nadeem also revealed that he is scheduled to meet with the Army Chief in the coming days.\", \"from\": 1789, \"to\": 1878, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1848, \"end\": 1852, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_Army\", \"score\": 0.9511590705600365, \"rank\": 0.050112731987718914, \"text\": \"Army\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q176799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_Army\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_Army\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nadeem\", \"from\": 1789, \"to\": 1795}, {\"ngram\": \"the coming days\", \"from\": 1862, \"to\": 1877}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When asked about the performance of athletes from India and Pakistan, he expressed his happiness, saying, \\\"I am glad to see athletes from both India and Pakistan showcasing their talent on the global stage.\\\"\", \"from\": 1879, \"to\": 2086, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1929, \"end\": 1934, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.9591801009984214, \"rank\": 0.03960601167688103, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1939, \"end\": 1947, \"title\": \"http://db